doctype html
head
  meta(charset='UTF-8')
  meta(name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0')
  title About Us - Price Information System
  style.
    body {
    background-color: #f5f5f5;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    }
    header {
    background-color: #333;
    color: white;
    padding: 15px 0;
    text-align: center;
    }
    .logo {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    }
    .logo img {
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
    margin-right: 10px;
    }
    .logo h1 {
    font-size: 1.5em;
    margin: 0;
    }
    nav {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 10px;
    }
    nav a {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: white;
    margin: 0 15px;
    font-weight: bold;
    }
    .about-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 50px auto;
    padding: 20px;
    background-color: white;
    border-radius: 5px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    footer {
    background-color: #333;
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 10px 0;
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 100%;
    }
header
  .logo
    img(src='logo.png' alt='logo')
    h1 Price Information System
  nav
    a(href='/home') Home
    a(href='/about') About Us
    a(href='/contact') Contact Us
    a(href='/login') Login
.about-content
  h2 About Us
  p
    | Welcome to the library management system. Our mission is to provide accurate and up-to-date information on prices for various products. We strive to empower consumers and businesses with valuable insights to make informed decisions.
  p
    | Our team is dedicated to delivering a reliable and user-friendly platform for accessing price information. We believe in transparency and efficiency, and we work towards creating a positive impact on the way people engage with pricing data.
  p
    | Thank you for choosing Price Information System. Feel free to explore our website and utilize the resources we provide.
footer
